Stranato gets angry, he is sitting around and his talent was being wasted! =
Stranato ran off and purposely locked himself in a freezer. Inzola asked Re=
ptilica and Bloodystrike to pardon her and ran after him, she searched the =
halls, and all around the base, but couldn't find him anywhere. An hour lat=
er, she hoped he wasn't dumb enough to lock himself in a freezer, or someth=
ing. She found him. Inzola is then sitting back in the room with Reptilica =
and Bloodystrike, making more weapons while Stranato is trying to warm up. =
His joints were frozen together. Stranato complained about something. Inzol=
a asked for another pardon and checked on him, his organic parts were freez=
er burnt

"Uhhh, you almost killed your organic parts by staying so long in=
 the freezer! They probably have a cold bug or something." Inzola said.

"T=
hat couldn't affect the rest of me, can it?" Stranato asked.

"I don't thin=
k so, your a robot, but just to make sure of something." Inzola said. She t=
ied him to a chair.

"Now don't move, just warm up." Inzola said. Stranato =
grumbled and fell asleep. He dreamed of him and Inzola in a peaceful meadow=
, when suddenly, an army crept over him, and Deemos appeared. Deemos kiled =
Inzola and held Stranato to watch it. Stranato wakes up and starts to squir=
m out of the ropes.

"Get these off of me, I have to go get Deemos!" Strana=
to yelled. Inzola tried to hold him down and was whispering to him. He didn=
't calm down one bit. He struggled and tried to get away, tried to get Deem=
os, gotta kill him! He had to get out of here and kill Deemos!

"That's it,=
 if you want to kill Deemos so bad, hold on." Inzola called Zardus on comml=
ink.

"Zardus, this is Inzola, Stranato seems to want action, he wants one =
of the Maximals, what should I do?" Inzola asked...
